	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天就是<delay8 />感恩节了。<delay20 />
我也难得从早上开始就坐立不安。<delay40 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你有没有<delay20 />准备好大吃特吃啊？<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这种<delay20 />能将一流厨师所做的菜肴
吃个痛快的日子<delay8 />可是十分难得的！<delay40 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嘿嘿，真是兴奋啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />终于<delay20 />翘首以盼的
