<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嘿，<delay8 />肚子都咕咕叫了～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00">毕竟是难得的感恩节，<delay20 />
